<section class="story" id="story" aria-label="Brand story">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="story__grid">
      <div class="story__text reveal-on-scroll-left">
        <span class="story__label">Our Origin</span>
        <h2 class="story__heading">Born from the silence between seasons</h2>
        <div class="story__divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <p class="story__body">
          VELOUR was not founded — it was <em>summoned</em>. In a stone atelier on the outskirts of Grasse,
          our master perfumer spent eleven years in solitude, deconstructing the invisible architecture of memory.
          Each fragrance in our collection is not merely a scent — it is a cartography of feeling, a map drawn
          in molecules.
        </p>
        <p class="story__body">
          We source our ingredients from the margins of the known world: aged oud from the
          rain-drenched forests of Assam, iris pallida cultivated for seven years in Tuscan clay,
          ambergris found on the volcanic shores of New Zealand. We do not compromise.
          We do not rush. We do not repeat.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="story__image-wrap reveal-on-scroll-right">
        <img
          src="/images/story-bg.png"
          alt="Inside the VELOUR atelier — vintage brass scales, amber bottles of essential oils, dried flowers and raw ingredients on a marble workbench, bathed in warm golden light"
          loading="lazy"
          width="600"
          height="750"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
